data.description: Welcome Home to this spectacular Marshall County walk out ranch. The home is situated on an oversized lot with trees lining the back of the property. The home boasts 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. 1st bedroom en suite walk in closet is a MUST SEE. Bright kitchen with newer appliances and butcher block counter tops. Dining room is spacious with loads of windows letting in the natural light. Lower level is perfect for entertaining and includes 2 bedrooms, craft room and entry to a beautiful enclosed screen porch. The back yard is an oasis for summer relaxation. Newer roof and HVAC system. Loads of updates and so much more!!
